query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('admin',
'alfresco',
'angular-ui-grid',
'apache-spark-mllib',
'arcgis',
'data-mining',
'delimiter',
'prestashop-1.6',
'redmine',
'startup',
'sticky',
'sybase',
'traits');
